reviewText:
A friend of mine brought "The Peculiarities of the National Fishing" a few weeks ago and I enjoyed it thoroughly, so then  I got the hunting one which made me wanting more.  So I found this one and I was not disappointed at all.  Very funny stuff.  Just when I thought the movie couldn't get any stranger, it did.

This movie was about some guys who were stuck in a hospital on New Year's Eve and their efforts to try and throw a party.
